---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Acne Program | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'A structured, customized plan that blends medical-grade skincare, in-office treatments, and coaching to clear acne, prevent scars, and maintain healthy skin.',
  canonical: '/services/acne-program/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Acne Program',
      serviceType: 'Dermatologic care',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/acne-program/',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      }
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Advanced Skin Care</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Acne Program</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        A structured, stepwise plan that combines targeted topicals, in-office procedures, lifestyle guidance,
        and regular check-ins to calm active breakouts, minimize post-inflammatory marks, and help prevent scars.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Approach</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Personalized, multi-modal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Ideal for</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Persistent or recurrent acne</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Timeline</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">4–8 wks to first changes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minimal (varies by step)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Acne is multifactorial, so single products rarely solve it long-term. Our Acne Program builds a
            comprehensive plan—combining home care, in-office treatments, and education—to reduce active lesions,
            calm inflammation, protect the skin barrier, and lower the risk of scarring and discoloration.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
            {[
              'Reduce inflammatory and non-inflammatory lesions',
              'Lower redness and post-breakout marks',
              'Protect against future breakouts',
              'Improve texture, tone, and confidence'
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                <span>{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Key benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Consistent, sustained results',
                'Lower relapse risk',
                'Scar prevention focus',
                'Adapted to your skin type',
                'Progress photos and check-ins',
                'Education and routine coaching'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Plans are individualized; medical therapies are used when appropriate and prescribed by your provider.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program components -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What the program can include</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Targeted topicals</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Retinoids, benzoyl peroxide, salicylic or azelaic acid</li>
              <li>Antibiotic or antibacterial combinations when indicated</li>
              <li>Barrier-safe routines to balance efficacy and tolerance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Oral/systemic options</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Short-course oral antibiotics for inflammatory flares</li>
              <li>Hormonal strategies (for appropriate candidates)</li>
              <li>Isotretinoin for severe or refractory cases (strict oversight)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">In-office procedures</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Chemical peels calibrated for acne-prone skin</li>
              <li>LED/light-based therapies; extractions when appropriate</li>
              <li>Texture work (e.g., SkinPen or microneedling) once acne is controlled</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Specific therapies depend on severity, skin tone, and medical history. Your provider will tailor a safe sequence and schedule.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline / phases -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Phases and timeline</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {[
            {
              title: 'Launch',
              time: 'Weeks 4–8',
              items: ['Introduce topicals', 'Reduce inflammation', 'Build tolerance']
            },
            {
              title: 'Build',
              time: 'Months 3–6',
              items: ['Layer therapies as needed', 'Add in-office support', 'Refine dosing']
            },
            {
              title: 'Consolidate',
              time: 'Months 6–12',
              items: ['Stabilize clear skin', 'Address marks/texture', 'Document progress']
            },
            {
              title: 'Maintain',
              time: 'Ongoing',
              items: ['Maintenance routine', 'Periodic touch-ups', 'Relapse prevention']
            }
          ].map(card => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-500">{card.time}</div>
              <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium text-neutral-900">{card.title}</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                {card.items.map(i => <li>{i}</li>)}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Many topicals take 4–8 weeks to show visible change; substantial improvement can take several months.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Your plan starts with a consultation, photos, and a barrier-friendly routine. We meet at set intervals
            to fine-tune products, consider procedures, and track outcomes. Clear communication keeps your skin on course.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Check-ins</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Progress photos and tolerance review</li>
                <li>Adjust strength, frequency, or add-ons</li>
                <li>Education on triggers and routine habits</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Results cadence</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Weeks 4–8: first visible changes</li>
                <li>Months 3–6: fewer flares; marks start to fade</li>
                <li>Months 6–12: texture and tone refine</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Care tips -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Care tips during the program</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Daily broad-spectrum SPF; avoid picking and harsh scrubs.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use non-comedogenic moisturizer to protect barrier.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Keep routines consistent; report irritation early.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Space actives as directed; don’t stack too many at once.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Follow timing around peels/laser per provider guidance.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Lifestyle: clean pillowcases, mindful makeup, gentle cleansing.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & precautions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">General</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Some oral therapies require medical supervision and labs.</li>
              <li>Avoid combining multiple strong actives without guidance.</li>
              <li>Pregnancy: certain products/medications are not advised.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Skin tone & sensitivity</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>We tailor peels and light therapies to minimize PIH risk.</li>
              <li>Disclose all allergies and photosensitizing medications.</li>
              <li>Report persistent redness or pain promptly for adjustments.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How soon will I see results?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              First changes often appear by weeks 4–8, with substantial gains over several months as inflammation settles and marks fade.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Do I have to do in-office treatments?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Not required for every case, but procedures like calibrated peels, LED, or extractions can accelerate results and improve texture.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is the program suitable for severe acne?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Yes. For severe or scarring acne, systemic options and closer follow-up may be included, with strict safety monitoring.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Are results permanent?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Acne can be chronic. The goal is sustained control and fewer relapses. Maintenance routines help preserve results.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to start a clear-skin plan tailored to you?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
